INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3000","letter","1776-12-26","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","I am well pleased to see the attention they pay General Lee - and I shall make it a point to collect and send your Excellency, soon as possible, the one hundred half Johannes they order.","ltr_rom3000.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,88,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3001","letter","1776-12-30","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","I have just received your favor of this day, and sent to General Putnam to detain the express until I collect the hard money you want, which you may depend shall be sent, in one specie or other, with this letter","ltr_rom3001.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,88,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3002","letter","1777-01-01","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","ever solicitous to comply with your requisitions, I am up very early this morning to despatch a supply of fifty thousand dollars to your Excellency.","ltr_rom3002.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,88,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3003","letter","1777-03-06","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","It is truly lamentable, that we have never been able to this day to conquer that fundamental error made in the outset by short enlistments.","ltr_rom3003.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,88,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3004","letter","1777-05-10","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","The bearer of this, the Marquis Armand de la Rouerie, is entitled to my warmest recommendations, because he brought from his own country letters to me that I am obliged to attend to, and put great faith in","ltr_rom3004.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,88,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3700","letter","1781-06-15","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","I am Financier electa, but that is all - for had I taken the oath and my commission, my seat in the Assembly must have been vacated. And I think it of the utmost consequence to preserve my right of appearing there","ltr_rom3700.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,59,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3701","letter","1781-08-28","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","I directed the Commissary-General, immediately on my return from camp, to cause the deposit of three hundred barrels of flour, three hundred barrels of salt meat, and twelve hogsheads of rum, to be made at the Head of Elk","ltr_rom3701.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,59,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom3702","letter","1782-01-26","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","George","Washington","","individual","","Recruiting the army is certainly of importance, and ought therefore to be urged upon the several States - but, should it be necessary to expend money for that purpose, it must not be considered as a part of the quota called for by Congress","ltr_rom3702.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,59,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom4000","letter","1781-06-05","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","John","Jay","","individual","","This campaign, as usual, opens to our disadvantage - but I expect it will also, as usual, close favourably for us. The vices and follies of our enemies may justly be counted among the number of our fast friends.","ltr_rom4000.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,37,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom4001","letter","1783-01-03","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","John","Jay","","individual","","I cannot take time at present to enter on any political discussions. But you must allow me to declare my perfect satisfaction in, and approbation of, your conduct in Europe.","ltr_rom4001.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,37,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom4002","letter","1783-11-27","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","John","Jay","","individual","","I congratulate you on the signing of the definitive treaty.. and on the evacuation of New- York, which took place on Tuesday. Our friend Gouverneur Morris is there.","ltr_rom4002.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,37,0);
INSERT INTO media VALUES ("ltr_rom4003","letter","1783-11-04","Philadelphia","PA","US","Robert","Morris","","John","Jay","","individual","","I acknowledge the force of all your observations on my intended resignation, and know the necessity of perseverance so long as there is a prospect of being useful","ltr_rom4003.txt","hans.brough@yahoo.com",NULL,20090802183836,NULL,37,0);
